    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a dedicated project. The engine currently has a loud knock and significant oil consumption, while the exterior shows heavy rusting on the wheel wells and several deep scratches. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and the electrical system is temperamental, with the power windows and radio currently non-functional. It is not recommended for daily use without extensive repairs.",
